info: Rating, 4 stars,  · May 2022,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
1. Location: There is a discrepancy on the map and the real address. Due to the message response, we couldn't contact the host, we wasted a lot of time finding a check-in point, and asked a lot of people who don't know where this building is, but because it is in the city, it is still convenient to go to every place
2. Environmental hygiene: The living room is clean and tidy
But no washing machine.
3. House equipment: A/C cools well
Fully furnished, but Wi-Fi can't be connected even if it is restarted, no internet
4. Price: The overall price is a little high, it may be that the decoration of the room is better, it would be better if the equipment was more complete.

rating_comment: This is the 2nd time i have rented a place through airbnb in chittagong. This apartment is bigger than as usual. no one to bother you. If you need help Mr. Faisal is a text away. and of course all the local communications you will be doing is Mr. Amin. He and his family is such a exceptional and a wonderful family to meet. Mr Amin was there every steps away if you need any help or any questions. I think everytime Come to chittagong this will be my home away from home. in This house what ever you need you will find it. Thank you Capt. Faisal for sharing your home with us.
